    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "We have explicit logic in the bridge repair code to kill blocking actors.  This has either regressed, or perhaps it was never set up to handle buildings (which work a bit different too other actors) properly.\n\nHaving the repair blocked based on actors that the player may not be able to see is inconsistent with with the fog/shroud, so IMO the former makes much more sense.\n"
